{"id": 2537, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪件事让你意识到，网上的自己“戳点”变高了？", "description": "面无表情点进去，再面无表情地出来。（题图来自：iStock ©️ ilyast）", "record_count": 2925, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180925162213swmxknrT7YDSlUWE.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-09T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 302848, "content": "任何带走有各种极端化形容词的标题，比如“史上最…”、“竟然…”、“顶级…”等，都没有任何兴致点进去看一眼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253166}, {"id": 302849, "content": "以前自己很爱看科技类新闻，36kr，虎嗅，黑马之类的，感觉看完很充实，现在越发觉得没用，还是踏踏实实把时间用来学专业能力比较好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598125}, {"id": 302852, "content": "我的回复😂😂😂\n实际表情😐😐😐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462357}, {"id": 302854, "content": "一脸冷漠的打出“哈哈哈哈哈哈”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465849}, {"id": 302855, "content": "越来越觉得某些新闻网的东西重复性高，而且无聊，想看书，但是有时又陷入用这些东西浪费时间的囧境", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280608}, {"id": 302857, "content": "所有回复都变成了👌", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465303}, {"id": 302858, "content": "任何事情都无所谓的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465919}, {"id": 300299, "content": "从“不看雷剧”到“连雷剧吐槽文都懒得看”", "image": null, "praise_count": 317, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 302859, "content": "看到黑我日婆的话不会生气 不会回复 不会和他撕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465952}, {"id": 300300, "content": "对很喜欢的博主，从“篇篇都看”到“只看标题，点不点正文看心情”", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 300301, "content": "看视频，15秒之内戳不中笑点就会叉掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 302861, "content": "网上大家都喜欢说一样的梗，看久了会觉得网络真无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052521}, {"id": 300302, "content": "“哈哈哈哈哈”、“笑哭” emoji 几乎每天都用，其实内心毫无波澜", "image": null, "praise_count": 597, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 304142, "content": "朋友圈早关了，关注的公众号三个以内", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1448114}, {"id": 302867, "content": "以前看到点世风日下的新闻就要转发大骂一通，现在已经心如止水", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462597}, {"id": 303891, "content": "当别人跟我说一些以为会把我震慑到的事而我早就经历过以至于已经无动于衷的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469494}, {"id": 302869, "content": "喝热水了，穿秋裤了，注意身体变化了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466041}, {"id": 302871, "content": "室友分享的很好笑的文字或者图片，其他室友都在哈哈大笑，我，面无表情看完，甚至不知道有什么可笑😊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466055}, {"id": 303128, "content": "骂鹿晗骂累了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463790}, {"id": 302873, "content": "看friends第二遍的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460339}, {"id": 302874, "content": "网红咖啡馆过时了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466096}, {"id": 302875, "content": "老子一眼就看出来你是在搏眼球！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466101}, {"id": 304667, "content": "励志故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240486}, {"id": 306459, "content": "求个Windows上的免费vpn 如果可以的话 谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281663}, {"id": 302876, "content": "对网络上的许多事物都心如止水", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456423}, {"id": 302877, "content": "连那么有意思的话题都没大心思看完评论，我可能不是戳点高，只是懒吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052677}, {"id": 302878, "content": "你拿给我看一段好笑的段子，我却只能仰着头附和着你笑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903504}, {"id": 303391, "content": "网上无论什么样的瓜 都没有兴趣吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449093}, {"id": 302881, "content": "类似35岁职场危机，下半生困苦之类的文章……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465027}, {"id": 302882, "content": "宠辱不惊 谁都看不出我的情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464755}, {"id": 302883, "content": "内心再慌乱也不说了，静等再乱也不慌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1439591}, {"id": 303140, "content": "这次的信小呆事件…营销味太浓了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437708}, {"id": 302886, "content": "哗众取宠的标题让我厌恶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464339}, {"id": 302887, "content": "看到百分之99的新闻消息段子 都内心平静", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466210}, {"id": 302891, "content": "从看电视剧，电影，综艺从不快进变成现在的丝毫不能容忍尿点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461606}, {"id": 302893, "content": "网络越普及，沙雕越多。见的多了，自然戳点就高了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1072117}, {"id": 302894, "content": "不管啥事，我都是一个字，淡定😏😏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426732}, {"id": 303150, "content": "看标题，猜内容，进入看，极相同，退出来，呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355256}, {"id": 302895, "content": "除了看爱豆 永远面无表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466260}, {"id": 302896, "content": "今日头条打开，下拉，关闭。\n微博打开，下拉，关闭。\nQQ空间打开，下拉，关闭。\n“真tm无聊。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463984}, {"id": 302897, "content": "说话总是安着自己的说话习惯，从来不模仿流行语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466285}, {"id": 302898, "content": "90后的我开始养生了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466295}, {"id": 302899, "content": "总是寻找表情，配合对方的文字", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466294}, {"id": 315699, "content": "某某因为.....成网红，看到这几个字能上头条，我都觉得是国家的悲哀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 302901, "content": "从评论转发点赞🤗到转发点赞😉到只点赞😏到一脸冷漠😐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455584}, {"id": 302902, "content": "千篇一律。即使在引人思考的部分也会有雷同的争论，毕竟这年头水军的行话也在进步。网上言论皆是如此，不如看看猫猫狗狗，为了人生赢家的梦想而奋斗。这可能就是所谓的盛极必衰吧，作为95后的我已经逐渐脱离网络世界了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458722}, {"id": 303158, "content": "哈哈哈家就", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573723}, {"id": 302904, "content": "从15年开始，不再追番了，发现新人新作新梗都不认识，可以点的文章新闻就少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636017}, {"id": 302905, "content": "对娱乐，八卦，没有兴趣了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466374}, {"id": 302906, "content": "从觉得手机很好玩不停地刷，到不管怎么刷都觉得很没意思，想干别的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466388}]}